rocessing. Further, we propose performance optimizations leveraging the\nfact that the output is noisy. We demonstrate Crypt$\\epsilon$'s feasibility for\npractical DP analysis with extensive empirical evaluations on real datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Feb 2019 20:00:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Nov 2019 00:04:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 Nov 2019 17:55:14 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2019 06:17:57 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 10 Mar 2020 04:35:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-11"}
