sparse data distribution, GSGM can perform a 37% improvement on\ntraining stability. Moreover, only GSGM can converge well when the number of\ncomputing nodes grows to 30, compared to the state-of-the-art distributed\nasynchronous algorithms. At the same time, GSGM is robust to different degrees\nof non-IID data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Feb 2019 02:39:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Mar 2019 06:42:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Apr 2019 09:05:44 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 07:58:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-03"}
